summary: You can now see teenagers throughout Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
You can now see teenagers throughout Skyrim adding life to the game. Teenagers can be killed and pickpocketed from since they are consider young adults. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1016/?]here[/url]. You should also check out [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75810?]Toddlers[/url]. And if you play Oblivion also look at my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/44095/?]Oblivion Teenagers[/url].

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin into your data folder
author: LegoManIAm94
